Rating: 4
I loved this recipe !! I made it for my gourmet group. I used organic sugar for the carmelization and slivered & toasted almonds in the bottom of 8 buttered ramikens in place of 1 large pan. I added a 1/2 teaspoon of almond extract to the flan and did not add the almonds to the flan mixture as called for in the recipe. The results were excellent !!

Rating: 4
Great, easy recipe. I didn't have a 9 inch round pan that was 3 inches high, so I used one that was 1 inch high. The flan just barely fit in, but it did make it easy to remove it onto the platter.